---

<MainLayout>
  <Mockup title="The Wheat Field" mockup={mockup}>
    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg">
      <p>
        "The Wheat Field" is an autobiographical 42-page graphic novel about my
        experiences while processing the grief of my grandparents passing. In
        anÂ attempt to reclaim some closeness to my grandmother, I go on an
        investigation into the hidden family history that she had been entrusted
        with shortly before her death.
      </p>

      <p>
        Below are excerpts form the graphic novel, if interested in reading more
        please reach out! I also sell single print editions of the full book -
        for all inquiries please reach out at miriamshbooks@gmail.com.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Mockup>

  <LightBox im={cover} class="mt-12 w-3/4 md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 mx-auto" />

